name: LadyRa/ Fantasy/ woman in armor
description:
This model was based on a 3D model of a girl working in armor. A mix of science fiction and fantasy, where a girl in a robotic suit and armor. In this case, these are more portraits, and they do not turn out to be full-length. I tried to do experiments with different models. The heroine of this model is Lady Ra, I hope you will like the generated images.

  • Base model - f222

  • max steps was - 4000

  • a close up of a woman wearing a helmet, robort, serious looking, portrait, rococo, looks straight ahead, glowing, realistic fantasy photography, dressed in light armor, soft diffuse lighting, in leather armor, female-focus, imperium, fantasy paladin woman,

  • <hypernet:LadyRa-3500:0.7> (7 and more)

  • Please leave feedback and images you manage to create with ❤

  • In full growth(body), of course, they no longer look so elegant, but different generations are quite not bad (^_~)
